{"tid":2014705,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"網媒記者被投訴涉違性別歧視　平機會籲當事人提供資料","createTime":"2020-05-13T07:44:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T08:59:16.000Z","uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4904c9456b18178728fe688193400244e23c561a","tid":2014705,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T07:44:52.000Z","msg":"網絡媒體《全民記者》被指上周日直播旺角示威期間，曾以粗言穢語描述女警身材。民建聯婦女事務委員會到平機會投訴，譴責有關行為侮辱女性，涉嫌違反性別歧視條例，並要求調查跟進。<br />\n<br />\n平機會署理營運總監朱崇文對事件表示關注，至於有關行為是否違法，則須視乎事件是否合符公眾範疇內的特定相關關係，如僱傭或教育關係。他呼籲當事人主動提供更多資料，當局方可跟進。<br />\n<br />\n記協亦表示已接獲相關投訴，對《全民記者》的不當行為表示遺憾，強調新聞從業員必須竭力保持客觀，並須注意有否違反新聞工作者的專業操守，《全民記者》事後於專頁發聲明道歉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1525898_1_L_20200513151048.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1525898_1_L_20200513151048.jpg&h=4f8ac7b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7737e9c61f30157c5247992d543692066763892","tid":2014705,"uid":54800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T07:46:37.000Z","msg":"葛帆煩你條臭..............<br />\n<br />\n又出黎抽水~~ <br />\n<br />\n本人呼籲女警當事人親身去平機會投訴~<br />\n最好開埋記招交待事件~!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c77d9e61782cb94d2d4454439c342180a2d5402","tid":2014705,"uid":228868,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T07:47:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gDTFv5s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgDTFv5s.png&h=00a936fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aeb0b0c876d676785dde78599c7488487a05e2d","tid":2014705,"uid":43062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T07:49:50.000Z","msg":"黃子悅呢仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><